				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I really need to release the next version of helpbot.php, it has all kinds of nice features with pop-ups, like if a reply is more than 200 characters, it will convert all the spam into a pop-up
<br />

<br />
also, I have a feature where you can make a file
<br />
/tell &lt;bot&gt; makefile filename message here\n1. step one\n2. step2
<br />

<br />
then when you do 
<br />
/tell &lt;bot&gt; showfile filename
<br />

<br />
you'll see
<br />
Bot: contents of "filename" &lt;= click here
<br />

<br />
and then you can click on "filename" and see this in your popup:
<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">message here
<br />
1. step one
<br />
2. step two</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><span style="font-weight: bold"> </span></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
